        <Parent_String>modified asphalt [300212329], asphalt (bituminous material) [300012966], bitumen (material) [300012976], natural bituminous material [300212198], bituminous material [300012964], organic material [300011792], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
